name: De Curtò 04. Veritas et virtus.
description: Artistic scenes featuring distinct species of flowers. The series Veritas et virtus introduces a set of synthetically generated images of blossoms imagined by Generative Adversarial Networks. This piece is generated by a method developed in 2017 (HDCGAN) by Curtò et al. The method was the state-of-the-art in synthetic image generation in 2017, and still is on some benchmarks. The code has not been released to the public. This is the fourth piece of this specific series that is minted. @DeCurto2
